<i>noun</i>: 양극 [양ː극] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>양극 [양ː극]</dt><br>
<dd>1. the positive and negative poles</dd><br>
<dd>양극과 음극.</dd><br>
<dd>The positive pole and the negative pole.</dd><br>
<dd>2. the two poles; the north and south poles</dd><br>
<dd>북극과 남극.</dd><br>
<dd>The north pole and the south pole.</dd><br>
<dd>3. extremes; both extremities</dd><br>
<dd>두 가지의 생각이나 행동 등이 서로 아주 먼 거리에 있거나 완전히 반대되는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which two ideas, acts, etc., are very distant from or absolutely opposite to each other.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>